# ========================================
# Homelas - Environment Variables
# ========================================

# Supabase Configuration
# Get these from: https://supabase.com/dashboard/project/_/settings/api
SUPABASE_URL=https://your-project.supabase.co
SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=your-anon-key-here

# NextAuth.js Configuration
# Generate AUTH_SECRET with: openssl rand -base64 32
AUTH_SECRET=your-auth-secret-here-run-openssl-rand-base64-32

# GitHub OAuth Configuration
# Create OAuth App at: https://github.com/settings/developers
# See GITHUB_OAUTH_SETUP.md for detailed instructions
AUTH_GITHUB_ID=your-github-oauth-app-id
AUTH_GITHUB_SECRET=your-github-oauth-app-secret

# ========================================
# Test User (Development Only)
# ========================================
# Para crear un usuario de prueba en desarrollo:
#   1. Copia este archivo: cp .env.example .env.local
#   2. Configura tus credenciales arriba
#   3. Ejecuta: npx tsx create-test-user.ts
#
# El script creará un usuario con credenciales de prueba
# que podrás usar para probar la aplicación localmente.
